Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,{Eyecatch}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.60,0:00:04.52,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.06,0:00:06.98,Main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.07,0:00:12.65,Flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You feeling lonely, Gear?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:17.99,Flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sad to see you going away, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.53,0:00:20.58,Flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,But it's dangerous here,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.58,0:00:22.54,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,and you don't want to cause \Ntrouble for people, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:26.83,Flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,So I have to send you somewhere safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.63,0:00:31.55,Flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,There are things you have to do, \Nwhether you like it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.17,0:00:34.51,Flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Someday you'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:35.43,Flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.05,0:00:37.43,Flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Stay safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.68,0:00:40.76,Flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,When I grow up, I'm joining the army.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:43.39,Flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to join the \Narmy and fight with you, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.69,0:00:49.98,Flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,By the time you grow up, \Nthe war will be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.61,0:00:53.07,Flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'll end it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.28,0:01:00.45,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.97,0:01:26.98,Title,G,0000,0000,0000,,Lost Star & {\c&H3FDCE1&}KID
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.02,0:01:29.36,Main,DF,0000,0000,0000,,So you're a decoy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.36,0:01:30.36,Main,DF,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:33.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The only things past me is the prison,\N and it's a dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.48,0:01:36.99,Main,DF,0000,0000,0000,,When the rest of them come back, \NI'll destroy them then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.74,0:01:39.37,Main,DF,0000,0000,0000,,Until then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:43.20,Main,DF,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have my fun with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.37,0:01:45.54,Main,Purple,0000,0000,0000,,No, you won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.67,0:01:50.63,Main,DF,0000,0000,0000,,What? An exploding round?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.92,0:01:53.75,Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:03.85,Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,What's your skin made out of?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.85,0:02:06.93,Main,DF,0000,0000,0000,,Your weak weapons can't touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:11.06,Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,If my bow won't work, \Nthen I don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:14.78,Main,DF,0000,0000,0000,,So you're going to surrender?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:15.57,Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:17.24,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,This is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.65,0:02:19.11,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try it on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.41,0:02:24.16,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,My new weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:27.79,Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,Shooting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.04,0:02:33.96,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:35.59,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.71,0:02:41.55,Main,DF,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me, the reason you were so \Nconfident is because you had Shooting?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.55,0:02:43.90,Main,DF,0000,0000,0000,,If it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.76,0:02:49.27,Main,DF,0000,0000,0000,,did I just crush your pride?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:51.90,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:54.52,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,Even if our Shooting is even,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:02:57.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,there are lots of things \NI'm better than him at.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.53,0:03:00.57,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:17.17,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,It hit him, so why didn't it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:18.71,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:20.63,Main,DF,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:24.76,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,that you can protect yourself \Nfrom Shooting with Force Field.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:25.93,Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.39,0:03:28.35,Main,DF,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:33.27,Main,DF,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take more than one of your \Nshots to break my Force Field!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.95,0:03:51.21,Main,DF,0000,0000,0000,,If you admit defeat, \NI won't continue to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:54.71,Main,DF,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather you be unhurt when I have fun with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:57.71,Main,DF,0000,0000,0000,,Admit defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:03:59.92,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,Admit defeat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:02.47,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:05.72,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't lost yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:09.97,Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,There are still things \NI'm better at than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:19.48,Main,DF,0000,0000,0000,,More exploding rounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:21.24,Main,DF,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:25.16,Main,DF,0000,0000,0000,,She hid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:27.03,Main,DF,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:30.24,Main,DF,0000,0000,0000,,No matter where you hide, \Nor where you attack from,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:32.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,it won't work on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:35.37,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,It's not much of a chance, \Nbut there's still hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:37.50,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,He said he could block one shot,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:42.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but if many hit him at the \Nsame time, it might work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:47.09,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,To fire a shot, I need to gather \Nlife energy in my fingers,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:49.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and keep it from overflowing \Nuntil I release it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:54.77,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,If I could store up many shots, \Ninstead of just one...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:57.31,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,I could maybe shoot a \NShot several times more
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:58.77,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,powerful than a regular one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:03.36,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,It's all speculation, \Nbut I won't know until I try.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:09.37,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,First gather the energy for one shot, \Nand then more...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:10.83,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.54,0:05:14.37,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,But it's really hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:16.96,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hold it in...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:19.04,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,The blood in my whole body is boiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:22.55,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,My fingernails are going to tear off... \N My fingers are about to break.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:25.05,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,But if I make the slightest \Nnoise, he'll find me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:28.55,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,This is hard... But if I don't charge up more,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:30.01,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to beat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:31.64,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,Enough for three shots!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:33.64,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.89,0:05:37.14,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:39.56,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hold it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:41.07,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:44.40,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can still do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:46.57,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,I'm better at this than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:49.03,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,I've held so much in for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:51.45,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,For such a long, long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:52.58,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:57.79,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,I can hold it in better than anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:02.46,Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:06.34,Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:11.60,7way,P,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,434)}7-way Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:25.36,Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,I won, somehow, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:29.24,Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,Holding it in isn't good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:37.45,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,I've not seen my dad \Nsince the day we said goodbye,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:39.87,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,and now he's right in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:42.13,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.79,0:06:44.67,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Gear?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.75,0:06:47.42,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You're alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:52.47,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you died during that attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:53.51,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:55.10,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:57.22,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:02.35,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to interrupt this emotional reunion, \Nbut there's no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:04.48,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,We'll continue the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:06.61,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:07.99,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,We need to get him out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:09.74,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,No, we don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:11.74,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,General Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:15.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Gear is going to absorb you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:16.99,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:21.62,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Ramses's orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:24.25,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,That's just like her. It's a good plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:26.09,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:27.50,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:30.26,Main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We're not going to save him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:32.72,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Absorb... what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:34.01,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:35.18,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,His life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:39.10,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,If the general was well, \Nwe were to rescue him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:44.52,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,But if he was hurt to the point \Nwhere he couldn't aid in the fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:48.11,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,you, his son, are to absorb his power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:51.03,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,That's our plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:52.15,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:54.07,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,We may still be able to save him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:55.03,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:57.79,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to take me back like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:07:59.58,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:02.83,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,If you move me, I'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:04.92,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:07.50,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:09.80,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Absorb me already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:13.01,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,To absorb someone, \Nyou need merely touch them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:17.22,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,If you touch them and think \Nabout wanting to absorb them,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:19.81,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,and they want to give you their life,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:22.35,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,you will absorb them in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:25.31,Flashback,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are Killers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:30.03,Flashback,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Any of you! Absorb me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:33.07,Flashback,P,0000,0000,0000,,You simply absorb.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:35.20,Flashback,P,0000,0000,0000,,Other's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:39.24,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to get better, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:41.83,Flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:46.50,Flashback,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that you could do \Nit if you tried, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:50.13,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:54.17,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I told you there'd be things \Nyou'd have to sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.17,0:08:56.09,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,if you want to be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:59.30,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the path you chose?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:02.06,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest Killer in Segua's army.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:05.44,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,He's the best person \Npossible to absorb.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:09.06,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be stronger, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:11.07,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,But not like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:15.90,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't just to make you stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:22.66,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's for Segua, and for \NGeneral Alex himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:25.41,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,For my dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:30.59,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,If he dies now, \Nhe leaves nothing behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:35.80,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,But if you absorb him, \Nhe will live on within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:41.64,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you, his son, \Ncarry on his power to stop
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:44.18,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,his death from being meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:48.52,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how insane it \Nis to end your reunion
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:50.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,with your father like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:54.61,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,But you understand, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:57.57,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What you really need to do right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:09:59.66,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,For Segua.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:01.83,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,For my dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:04.62,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's not what I want to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:07.96,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,There are things you have to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:12.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,whether you like it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:16.38,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Someday you'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:24.35,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:25.98,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What's stopping you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:28.14,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:31.65,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.31,0:10:33.77,Italics,G,0000,0000,0000,,When this happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:37.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,meeting my father and learning about \Nthe Killers was all just so sudden,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:39.86,Italics,G,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like it was a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:42.83,Italics,G,0000,0000,0000,,But I knew what I had to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:47.66,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I can relax, \NI'm getting sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:49.16,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:53.21,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Accept my power, Gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:55.75,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Gear...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:58.09,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Before I entrust everything to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:01.01,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,there's something you need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.89,0:11:05.35,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, Segua had two Killers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:09.89,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,We were the Segua Army's main force and always fought on the front lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:12.77,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,We were bound by tighter bonds than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:15.36,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,But one day we were badly wounded,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:17.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and surrounded by the \Nenemy with nothing left to do
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:18.90,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but wait for death.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:21.61,Flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,So the two of us are \Ngoing to die together?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:25.20,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No, there's still a way to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:30.04,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,If one of us absorbs the \Nother's life and power,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:31.50,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,they may be able to break \Nthrough the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.87,0:11:34.25,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,But this plan was an awful one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:36.25,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,One of us would die,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:39.72,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,and the other would lose \Nsomeone they cared about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:42.80,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't decide who would die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:45.76,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't decide at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:51.27,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,So in the end we chose an insane way
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:54.27,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,to decide who would kill the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:11:58.15,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of Gear for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:09.70,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,The great power I gained from absorbing \Nthe one I loved let me survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:16.00,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Even after I made it home alive, \Nmy regrets never left me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:19.05,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I sent you \Naway from the battle
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:22.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,when you were young was \Nbecause I was afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:25.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,of having someone I \Ncared about so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:31.14,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to ensure my loved ones \Nwere never caught in the fight again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:36.19,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,So I wanted to keep all \Nof them away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.56,0:12:38.86,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:41.90,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Even in the very end,\N I'm still making you suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:44.95,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no father at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:48.20,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:50.54,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:55.46,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,I was happy... I was happy \Nto see you in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:57.50,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:12:59.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:03.80,Italics,G,0000,0000,0000,,My dad gave me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:07.30,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,the greatest power in the Segua Army,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:10.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and the resolve to accept whatever \Nhappened, no matter awful it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:13.18,Italics,G,0000,0000,0000,,He gave me those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:32.24,Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,My whole body feels \Nnumb and I can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:35.00,Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,I hope the enemy doesn't find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:37.96,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh... Well, what do we have here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:41.46,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,D. Fisher bought it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:44.05,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:46.63,Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:50.64,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Did you kill Fisher?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:51.72,Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:54.14,Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the Tatoland army \Nisn't that strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:55.35,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:14:01.11,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty impressive, girl, \Nkilling that monster all by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:02.27,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:06.36,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you can't move now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:09.03,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,We have to ask you a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:11.91,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,You're in for a lot of torture later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:14.87,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:17.92,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}You're hot enough that torturing \Nyou will be lots of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:30.34,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,Gear...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:33.39,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Opal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:36.64,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,The mission is complete, Opal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:38.52,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:41.36,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you just came \Nfrom the prison,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:43.52,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't see General Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:46.90,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me guess: you came to absorb him,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:50.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but you freaked out and despaired \Nwhen you saw him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:51.87,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,He's Boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:53.37,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Bays's younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:54.83,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:58.25,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Boys, the younger brother \Nof the ultimate warrior, Bays.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:15:01.79,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who defeated General Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:05.88,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm the one who \Ntortured him down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:09.80,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,He never said anything, \Nso I accidentally overdid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:11.55,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,But what did you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:14.43,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,He was torn apart so badly,\N it was practically a form of art,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:16.18,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,but he was still barely alive, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.18,0:15:19.06,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,That's what makes me \Na genius at torture!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:21.06,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Tejirof, the mission's over, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:21.48,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I'd have \Nmore fun with a girl—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:31.61,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,You told me when the mission was over \NI could fight all I wanted, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:33.07,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:38.12,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,This was the birth of \NSegua's new messiah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:47.84,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to fight here until \NI've taken over Hope Fortress!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:51.30,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,My, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:53.34,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll fight a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.51,0:15:55.47,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Nel, take care of Opal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:57.14,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going for a bit, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:15:58.60,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:00.60,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to finish things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:02.60,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,In battle and you-know-what,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:04.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,taking care of them when \Nyou're done is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:08.11,Main,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:13.32,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,I can't leave my dad's body like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:17.37,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take over this fortress!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:27.92,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:29.92,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,So you made it out \Non your own after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:31.05,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:33.55,Main,Ba,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't have much else to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:36.10,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,The mission succeeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.10,0:16:37.14,Main,Ba,0000,0000,0000,,Did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:41.10,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,One of ours is kicking butt inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:47.65,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,But well, I figured if you interrupted him,\N he wouldn't be able to finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:50.82,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll finish you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:53.36,Main,Ba,0000,0000,0000,,Finish me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:55.70,Main,Ba,0000,0000,0000,,This time I won't let my guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:57.53,Main,Ba,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get the drop on me this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:17:00.79,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're strong and I \Ndon't want to fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:06.04,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I really didn't want to get serious \Nin a fight I was just hired on for...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:10.50,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,But if he's working that hard, \Nthen I think I should, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:14.26,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I can do anything I want, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:24.81,Main,Ba,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.81,0:17:25.85,Main,Ba,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:29.77,Main,Ba,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Tatoland lost \Nthis fight anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:31.82,Main,Ba,0000,0000,0000,,I'll withdraw for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.82,0:17:33.24,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:36.11,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll leave, that makes this easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:38.32,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:40.33,Main,Ba,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.04,0:17:43.58,Main,Ba,0000,0000,0000,,That wall of light you used to seal me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:44.33,Main,Ba,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:45.71,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:47.58,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,That's a type of Puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:49.50,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Puzzle Magic Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:52.59,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I learned all the \Ntechniques I use there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:55.22,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,If you're interested, drop by.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:57.51,Main,Ba,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:05.93,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Segua wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:11.02,Italics,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Gear's attack drove the \Nenemy from Hope Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:14.32,Italics,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,And the battle of Hope Fortress ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:36.05,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, Gear came \Nto the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:39.80,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to save him from the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:41.97,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.22,0:18:45.31,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You did everything you could.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:49.27,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You did everything I would've \Nhoped for, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:51.19,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You must be tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:54.86,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Our time is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:19:00.78,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave Segua... to our son.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:06.33,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.29,0:19:09.29,Italics,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,After the battle of Hope Fortress,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:13.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Segua lost its hero, General Alex,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:16.55,Italics,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,but the whole country was excited
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.55,0:19:19.22,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,over the arrival of their new hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:22.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and their first major \Nvictory in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:24.35,Italics,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,And the rumors of the \NSegua warrior who took
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:27.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope Fortress spread over the \Nwhole continent in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.93,0:19:30.81,Main,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,People called him "Blue Sonic."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:32.81,Locales,Ba,0000,0000,0000,,Tatoland
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:34.57,Main,Ba,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Mister, it didn't work this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:38.57,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Sometimes you win, \Nand sometimes you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:42.32,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}We can retake Hope Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:45.33,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}This is getting fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:50.58,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}There's plenty more fun to be had \Non the continent of Consume.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:50.08,Names,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(506,511)}Ruler of Tatoland and the Legendary Invader\N\N\N\N\N\N\N{\fs22}I. Vazer
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.58,0:19:52.33,Locales,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Havid Republic
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:54.71,Main,CEO,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Destruction is the \Nbeginning of creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:19:56.92,Main,CEO,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The die has been cast.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:20:00.42,Names,CEO,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(499,507)}Havid Republic Samurai CEO\N\N\N\N\N\N\N{\fs22}Kichou
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:20:00.76,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}We will be the ones to build \Na new era: Kichou Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:03.59,Locales,,0000,0000,0000,,Ganp Federation
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:03.59,Main,MuscleGirl,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Blue Sonic?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.89,0:20:06.85,Main,MuscleGirl,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I didn't know there was anyone that \Nstrong still on the continent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.43,0:20:14.44,Names,MuscleGirl,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(523,503)}Ganp Federation Wave Motion Warrior\N\N\N\N\N\N\N{\fs22}Tofig
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:14.48,Main,MuscleGirl,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}If he's stronger than I am, \NI'd love to meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:16.36,Locales,MuscleGirl,0000,0000,0000,,Kingdom of Slovia
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:21.36,Main,NeedsToFindPantsGirl,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Segua? I'm not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:26.12,Names,NeedsToFindPantsGirl,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Kingdom of Slovia Ultimate Queen\N\N\N\N\N\N\N{\fs22}Crystal
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:26.33,Main,NeedsToFindPantsGirl,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The only man I want to defeat is him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:30.87,Locales,NeedsToFindPantsGirl,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(529,500)}Elil Republic
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:31.83,Main,SomeOtherGirl,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}That's another big one \Nyou hunted today!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.83,0:20:35.38,Main,SomeOtherGirl,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Are you fired up because you're\Nconcerned about Segua?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:37.59,Main,SomeOtherGirl,0000,0000,0000,,You're not?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:40.13,Main,SomeOtherGirl,0000,0000,0000,,You're concerned about Segua, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:41.97,Main,SomeOtherGirl,0000,0000,0000,,You're not?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:46.64,Main,SomeOtherGirl,0000,0000,0000,,But you're thinking about the guy \Nthey call Blue Sonic, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.64,0:20:49.64,Names,SomeOtherGirl,0000,0000,0000,,Elil Republic Hero \N\N\N\N\N\N\N{\fs22}Myomuto
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:49.10,Main,Mu,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.89,0:20:55.02,Locales,Gamblers,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Ninteldo Empire Gambling Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:54.23,Main,Gamblers,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hey, who's that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:55.85,Main,Gamblers,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:59.07,Main,Gamblers,0000,0000,0000,,And supposedly he just \Nlearned the rules today!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:02.24,Main,Zelig,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing great today!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:03.40,Main,Fey,0000,0000,0000,,Zelig?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:04.70,Main,Fey,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:07.57,Main,Fey,0000,0000,0000,,You really were playing \Nhere, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.57,0:21:09.37,Main,GreenArmor,0000,0000,0000,,Know your role.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.37,0:21:11.70,Main,GreenArmor,0000,0000,0000,,You're the general of the armies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:12.91,Main,Z,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:16.63,Main,Z,0000,0000,0000,,So does this mean it's \Ntime to get going?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.63,0:21:18.42,Main,Gamblers,0000,0000,0000,,That's the genius, General Zelig?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:21.05,Main,Z,0000,0000,0000,,We're taking four generals?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:22.92,Main,Z,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:25.88,Names,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninteldo 6 Generals : Infinite Warrior\N\N\N\N\N\N\N{\fs22}Karvey
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:25.88,Main,Ka,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Yeah, let's go, Zelig.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:28.14,Main,Far,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I wouldn't underestimate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:30.68,Names,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Ninteldo 6 Generals: Miss Reset\N\N\N\N\N\N\N{\fs22}Fae
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.55,0:21:31.14,Main,Far,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Overconfidence brings destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.56,0:21:34.27,Main,GreenArmor,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Just don't forget the words of Marcus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.97,0:21:35.98,Names,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Ninteldo Six Generals: Royal Prince\N\N\N\N\N\N\N{\fs22}Guligi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.64,0:21:36.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Ninteldo has but one goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:41.07,Names,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Ninteldo Six Generals: The Man Who Solves All Mysteries\N\N\N\N\N\N\N{\fs22}Zelig
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.48,0:21:40.11,Main,Z,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Guess we'll go finish this, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:47.91,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there, hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:50.70,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing out here alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.33,0:21:52.45,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Playing with yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.87,0:21:53.95,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Tejirof?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.12,0:21:56.50,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking pretty normal, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.92,0:21:59.08,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd be more depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.50,0:22:03.17,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,About my dad? Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.84,0:22:05.38,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,I was ready for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.80,0:22:09.47,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, maybe I'm more happy than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.05,0:22:15.02,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting and winning made \Nsomeone I know so happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.43,0:22:18.15,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,But I still don't really \Nunderstand things.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.52,0:22:21.48,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Too much has happened at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.94,0:22:23.03,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.44,0:22:25.99,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,But that's the path you chose.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.20,0:22:27.11,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.11,0:22:30.74,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody will admire you just \Nbecause you're strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.28,0:22:34.91,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,People respect the ones that \Nchoose the difficult path,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.37,0:22:37.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,even if they're weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.08,0:22:41.46,Flashback,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,Stronger than anyone. Faster. Cooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.88,0:22:43.88,Flashback,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,I could never be like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.88,0:22:47.01,Flashback,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,You really amaze me, brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:50.18,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't respect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.72,0:22:52.85,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.51,0:22:56.31,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,But even so... \NI'm going to keep running.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.10,0:23:00.31,Main,G,0000,0000,0000,,To the center of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.31,0:23:02.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,